According to Absor, this rollback was just to make sure it didn't go live in today's patch.<br>
<br>
They still intend to change charms.<br>
<br>
[quote]I just wanted to let you know that the changes to charm spells were indeed removed from Test. We wanted to revert the code and make sure it was all ready for the patch tomorrow, without these changes included. 

However, we are still looking at changes along these lines. We just wanted more time with the changes on test before making any final decisions. 

A[/quote]<br>
